{"article_id":"BNCnGyZr2XuMNd1I","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The White House said Thursday","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"that it wants to see money for President Trump ' s border wall included in the spending bill","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"Congress must pass next week","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"- a demand","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"Democrats said","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"sours negotiations","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"and makes a government shutdown more likely .","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"The demands mark a reversal for the administration ,","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"which had been saying","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"it found enough money","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"to build prototypes this year","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"and wouldn ' t need a major infusion of cash until next year .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"But White House Budget Director Mick Mulvaney said in an interview with The Associated Press on Wednesday","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"that the wall and the money for more immigration agents are priorities .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"\" We know","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"there are a lot of people on the Hill , especially in the Democratic Party ,","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"who don ' t like the wall ,","depth":11},{"id":17,"text":"but they lost the election .","depth":11},{"id":18,"text":"And the president should ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"I think ,","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"at least have the opportunity","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"to fund one of his highest priorities in the first funding bill under his administration , \"","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"Mr. Mulvaney said .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"The White House issued its demand","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"just days after Democrats insisted","depth":6},{"id":25,"text":"that the spending bill include billions of dollars","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"to prop up Obamacare .","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"Democratic aides signaled","depth":5},{"id":28,"text":"that they wouldn ' t accept a bill","depth":6},{"id":29,"text":"without the cost-sharing payments","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"intended to keep insurers invested in the health care law .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"With Mr. Mulvaney ' s demand , both sides now appear to be entrenching .","depth":3},{"id":32,"text":"\" Everything had been moving smoothly","depth":6},{"id":33,"text":"until the administration moved in with a heavy hand , \"","depth":6},{"id":34,"text":"said Matt House , a spokesman for Senate Minority Leader Charles E. Schumer , New York Democrat .","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"\" Not only are Democrats opposed to the wall ,","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"there is significant Republican opposition as well . \"","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"Congress is once again on the clock ,","depth":6},{"id":38,"text":"racing an April 28 deadline","depth":7},{"id":39,"text":"for passing a funding bill","depth":8},{"id":40,"text":"to last the rest of the fiscal year ,","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"which ends Sept. 30 .","depth":9},{"id":42,"text":"Without a bill ,","depth":6},{"id":43,"text":"the government would face a partial shutdown","depth":7},{"id":44,"text":"ending nonessential services .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"The Trump White House will begin issuing plans to agencies Friday in preparation for a shutdown .","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"It would be the second shutdown in four years .","depth":6},{"id":47,"text":"In 2013 , congressional Republicans orchestrated a shutdown","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"to try to stop funding of Obamacare .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"That 16-day shutdown ended","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"after Republicans conceded .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Democrats are convinced","depth":8},{"id":52,"text":"that Republicans would be blamed for a shutdown this time as well .","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"As the minority party , though , Democrats would play the bigger role","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"in mounting an obstruction .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Mr. Trump , at a press conference Thursday , said","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"he is not angling for a shutdown .","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"\" As far as keeping the government open ,","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"I think","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"we want to keep the government open .","depth":9},{"id":60,"text":"Don ' t you agree ? \"","depth":7},{"id":61,"text":"he told reporters .","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"Mr. Trump promised a border wall during the presidential election campaign","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"and asserted","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"that Mexico would pay for it .","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"He now acknowledges","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"that U.S. taxpayers will foot the bill upfront .","depth":7},{"id":67,"text":"Some lawmakers in Washington have questioned","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"whether a wall is needed .","depth":8},{"id":69,"text":"During the first two months of Mr. Trump ' s administration , there has been an astounding drop in the flow of people","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"attempting to jump the southwestern border .","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"Trump administration officials take credit for the drop ,","depth":13},{"id":72,"text":"saying","depth":14},{"id":73,"text":"the president ' s get-tough rhetoric has changed the calculations of would-be migrants from Latin America ,","depth":14},{"id":74,"text":"but they insist","depth":13},{"id":75,"text":"the wall is needed","depth":14},{"id":76,"text":"to make sure","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"those gains are maintained .","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"\" It ' s absolutely essential that we build a wall , \"","depth":13},{"id":79,"text":"Homeland Security Secretary John F. Kelly said","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"as he toured the border in El Paso , Texas , on Thursday with Attorney General Jeff Sessions .","depth":14},{"id":81,"text":"Mr. Kelly said","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"a wall must be combined with technology and agents","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"to back it up .","depth":14},{"id":84,"text":"His department has found $ 20 million in funding","depth":11},{"id":85,"text":"that it will use","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"to build wall prototypes .","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"Bids were due earlier this month ,","depth":13},{"id":88,"text":"and officials say","depth":14},{"id":89,"text":"testing will take place this summer in San Diego .","depth":14},{"id":90,"text":"The prototypes have to be at least 18 feet high ,","depth":14},{"id":91,"text":"though 30 feet is the preferred height ,","depth":14},{"id":92,"text":"and should be able to withstand breaching attempts for up to four hours ,","depth":14},{"id":93,"text":"according to the contracting documents .","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"The wall also must look imposing ,","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"the documents said .","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"Senate Democrats this week released a report","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"the wall could stretch 1,827 miles , or most of the way across the 1,950-mile border , at a cost of nearly $ 70 billion .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"Homeland Security officials said","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"until they decide on a final design and locations ,","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"they can ' t begin to make an estimate","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"- though they said","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"the Democrats ' figures were baseless extrapolations .","depth":11},{"id":104,"text":"One immigration analyst said","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"the administration had been taking a low-key approach to wall funding until early this week ,","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"when it suddenly became a priority in negotiations .","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"It could be a bargaining chip","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"designed to counter Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"who just last week insisted","depth":11},{"id":110,"text":"that the Obamacare money be included .","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"Mr. Mulvaney said","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"neither he nor Mr. Trump is enthused about the Obamacare money","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"but that they could accept it","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"if Democrats are willing to deal on Republican priorities .","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"\" If it ' s important enough to the Democrats ,","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"we ' d be happy to talk to them about including that in sort of some type of compromise , \"","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"the budget director told AP .","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s immigration plans have been among the most controversial issues of his young administration .","depth":3},{"id":119,"text":"Immigrant rights activists this week complained","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"that his agents deported an illegal immigrant Dreamer , 23-year-old Juan Manuel Montes ,","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"who was supposed to be protected under Mr. Obama ' s 2012 deportation amnesty .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"Mr. Kelly ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"speaking at the border ,","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"said","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"Mr. Montes was deported back to Mexico","depth":9},{"id":126,"text":"after breaking terms of the amnesty ,","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"known officially as Deferred Action for Childhood Arrivals , or DACA .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"\" There was a time in his life","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"that this individual was a DACA resident ,","depth":11},{"id":130,"text":"but he gave that up by his behavior and his illegal actions .","depth":10},{"id":131,"text":"He ' s no longer covered by the DACA arrangement , \"","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Mr. Kelly said .","depth":8},{"id":133,"text":"The secretary didn ' t specify those illegal actions ,","depth":8},{"id":134,"text":"but his department this week said","depth":8},{"id":135,"text":"Mr. Montes had amassed several convictions","depth":9},{"id":136,"text":"for driving","depth":10},{"id":137,"text":"without a license","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"and one conviction for shoplifting .","depth":8},{"id":139,"text":"In addition , Mr. Montes left the U.S.","depth":7},{"id":140,"text":"without permission ,","depth":8},{"id":141,"text":"which was a violation of DACA .","depth":8},{"id":142,"text":"The young man ' s defenders , though , said","depth":6},{"id":143,"text":"the Homeland Security Department is fabricating its case .","depth":6},{"id":144,"text":"\" Right now , Trump agents are lying about Juan ' s story .","depth":8},{"id":145,"text":"They are smearing his name , \"","depth":8},{"id":146,"text":"said Greisa Martinez Rosa , advocacy director for United We Dream , a group","depth":8},{"id":147,"text":"that defends DACA recipients .","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"She compared Mr. Montes ' s deportation to race-related police slayings .","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"\" What they are doing to Juan is the same thing","depth":9},{"id":150,"text":"abusive law enforcement do to people of color","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"who are killed , \"","depth":10},{"id":152,"text":"she said .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":305,"left":189,"right":304,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":183,"right":188,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":175,"right":182,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":175,"left":159,"right":174,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":159,"left":0,"right":158,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":158,"left":154,"right":157,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":154,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":157,"left":155,"right":156,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":155,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":156,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":174,"left":163,"right":173,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":163,"left":7,"